@page
@model Ceng382.Pages.PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="pg-head">
    <h1 class="pg-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="pg-sub">Last updated @DateTime.Now.Year</p>
</div>

<div class="card" style="max-width:680px;">
    <div class="ch">
        <span class="ch-dot" style="background:#8b5cf6;"></span>
        <span class="ch-title">Data Usage</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cb">
        <p class="sec-text" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
            This application is a university lab project (CENG 382). It collects minimal user data only for authentication and feature demonstration.
        </p>

        <p class="sec-label">What we collect</p>
        <ul class="sec-list">
            <li>Email address and hashed password for authentication.</li>
            <li>Optional full name and profile photo provided at registration.</li>
            <li>Images uploaded through the gallery feature.</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="sec-label">How it's used</p>
        <ul class="sec-list">
            <li>User identity and session management only.</li>
            <li>Displaying uploaded content within the application interface.</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="sec-label">Storage</p>
        <p class="sec-text">All data is stored in a local SQLite database on the server. No data is shared with third parties.</p>
    </div>
</div>
